<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <%- include('partials/head') %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include('partials/nav') %>
    <main>
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="container hero-inner">
          <p class="eyebrow">The AI Guy</p>
          <h1>Technology that starts with your business problem</h1>
          <p class="lead">
            TAIG partners with organizations to clarify challenges, assess operations,
            and apply technology where it creates measurable business value — not complexity for its own sake.
          </p>
          <div class="hero-actions">
            <a href="/services" class="btn btn-primary">Explore Services</a>
            <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-secondary">Get in Touch</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section">
        <div class="container narrow">
          <h2>Our Mission</h2>
          <p>
            We exist to help businesses make better technology decisions. Too often, organizations
            adopt tools before they understand the problem. TAIG reverses that pattern — we listen first,
            diagnose clearly, and recommend solutions that fit how your business actually works.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section section-alt">
        <div class="container">
          <h2 class="section-title">Why Work With TAIG</h2>
          <div class="card-grid card-grid-3">
            <article class="card">
              <h3>Problem-First Approach</h3>
              <p>Every engagement begins with understanding your situation — not selling a predefined package.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="card">
              <h3>Practical Expertise</h3>
              <p>From day-to-day IT support to strategic advisory, we bring hands-on experience across operations and technology.</p>
            </article>
            <article class="card">
              <h3>Business Outcomes</h3>
              <p>We measure success by whether your people can work more effectively — not by how much technology we deploy.</p>
            </article>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section nebula-section">
        <div class="container narrow">
          <p class="eyebrow">Nebula</p>
          <h2>Clarity before solutions</h2>
          <p>
            Nebula is how TAIG maps your business landscape before recommending any technology.
            Think of it as a structured conversation about your goals, your daily operations,
            and the friction points holding you back.
          </p>
          <p>
            Rather than jumping to tools or trends, Nebula helps us — and you — see the full picture.
            The result is guidance grounded in your real context, so every next step has a clear purpose.
          </p>
          <a href="/about#nebula" class="text-link">Learn more about our approach &rarr;</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="section cta-band">
        <div class="container cta-band-inner">
          <h2>Ready to start with the problem?</h2>
          <p>Tell us what you're facing. We'll help you figure out the right path forward.</p>
          <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact TAIG</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>
    <%- include('partials/footer') %>
    <script src="/js/main.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
